reapack.desc: Export stems from multiple REAPER projects with UI-based track selection

version.author: stefan-tradingbot
version.changelog:
## [1.0.0] (2025-11-20)
### Features * Initial release with UI-based track selection * Users can now select which tracks to export via a graphical dialog instead of hardcoded track names * Supports multiple open projects with unified track selection * Interactive checkbox interface with "Select All" and "Deselect All" buttons * Scrollable track list for projects with many tracks
### Usage 1. Open all REAPER projects you want to export 2. Run the script 3. Select tracks to export in the dialog 4. Click OK to start the export process
